{"id":212301,"date":"2025-01-08T11:27:18","date_gmt":"2025-01-08T17:27:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/?page_id=212301"},"modified":"2025-05-07T10:12:50","modified_gmt":"2025-05-07T15:12:50","slug":"app-releases","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/app-releases\/","title":{"rendered":"Ditch Assist App Download"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"et_pb_section_0 et_pb_section et_section_regular et_flex_section et_pb_section_parallax\"><span class=\"et-pb-parallax-wrapper\"><span class=\"et-pb-parallax-background et-pb-parallax-background-module--divi-section-0\" style=\"background-image:url(https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/Ditch_Assist_Ideal_Ditch_Overlay.jpg)\"><\/span><\/span><span class=\"et_pb_background_mask\"><\/span>\n<div class=\"et_pb_row_0 et_pb_row et_flex_row preset--module--divi-row--5138c454-be54-4233-bd3b-f8e6a8747976\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_0 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone preset--module--divi-column--73121f80-a3ef-4484-8763-c3f18e3c56d2\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_heading_0 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-heading--f0c675ea-2574-4d0e-b725-30f8550a8550\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h4 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Download the Latest Ditch Assist App VERSION<\/h4><\/div><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_heading_1 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-heading--ddeb8c09-9078-4424-bc15-2efb6572e28e\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h1 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Get the Ditch Assist Android Apps Here<\/h1><\/div><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_text_0 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--2c55a9c4-feed-423b-9edb-ae0b5b365cac\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p><strong>We\u2019re excited to continue providing you with advanced functionality that&#8217;s easy to use through the Ditch Assist app. To serve our users better, we\u2019ve decided to make the Ditch Assist apps available exclusively through our website and no longer through the Play Store.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>This change allows us to:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Simplify Access<\/strong>: Avoid requiring Google accounts for downloads, giving you more control and convenience.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Support Older Devices<\/strong>: By distributing the app directly, we can ensure compatibility with a broader range of devices, including older ones that may no longer be supported on the Google Play Store.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Provide Better Service<\/strong>: Direct downloads enable us to update and improve the app faster without the restrictions imposed by third-party platforms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>While we\u2019ve enjoyed working with the Google Play Store in the past, their recent policies have made it difficult to meet the needs of all our users around the world. This shift to a direct-download approach ensures that more users, regardless of their device, can continue to receive the latest updates of the Ditch Assist app.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_1 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_column_empty et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone preset--module--divi-column--73121f80-a3ef-4484-8763-c3f18e3c56d2\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_section_1 et_pb_section et_section_regular et_flex_section\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_row_1 et_pb_row et_flex_row preset--module--divi-row--5138c454-be54-4233-bd3b-f8e6a8747976\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_2 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone preset--module--divi-column--73121f80-a3ef-4484-8763-c3f18e3c56d2\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_heading_2 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-heading--c33f07d9-41e0-421a-8799-5799df695cce\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h2 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Current Ditch Assist App Releases<\/h2><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_row_2 et_pb_row et_flex_row\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_3 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_blurb_0 et_pb_blurb et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_center et_pb_blurb_position_top et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-blurb--212b201d-2c34-41bd-936c-851b7357d08b\"><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_content et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_main_blurb_image\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon et-waypoint et_pb_animation_off et_pb_animation_off_tablet et_pb_animation_off_phone\">\uf135<\/span><\/span><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_container\"><h4 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Long-Term Stable Release<\/h4><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_description\"><p>The current long-term stable release is equivalent to the previous Play Store mainstream version. This version has been extensively tested by both our team and our user base, offering the most reliable and polished experience for everyday use. It is recommended for most users.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_heading_3 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h1 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Version: 4.22.4<\/h1><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_4 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_blurb_1 et_pb_blurb et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_center et_pb_blurb_position_top et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_content et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_main_blurb_image\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><sp