till contain some issues and bugs. This version is ideal for users who want to explore new functionality and provide feedback to help shape future updates.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_heading_4 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h1 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Version: 4.27.2<\/h1><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_7 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_blurb_3 et_pb_blurb et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_center et_pb_blurb_position_top et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_content et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_main_blurb_image\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon et-waypoint et_pb_animation_top et_pb_animation_top_tablet et_pb_animation_top_phone\">p<\/span><\/span><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_container\"><h4 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Features &#038; Functions<\/h4><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_description\"><ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>Auto Download of IDM Flow Maps<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>Auto Nudge Beta<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>Set Implement Width<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_8 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_1_wrapper\"><a class=\"et_pb_button_1 et_pb_button et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\" href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/app_releases\/com.AutoBotz.DitchAssist.v4.27.2.apk\" data-icon=\"\ue092\">Download Current Beta Release<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_row_4 et_pb_row et_flex_row\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_9 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_blurb_4 et_pb_blurb et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_center et_pb_blurb_position_top et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-blurb--212b201d-2c34-41bd-936c-851b7357d08b\"><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_content et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_main_blurb_image\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon et-waypoint et_pb_animation_off et_pb_animation_off_tablet et_pb_animation_off_phone\">\uf0c3<\/span><\/span><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_container\"><h4 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Current Alpha Release<\/h4><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_description\"><p>The alpha release is a preview version containing beta and experimental features or functionality that are still in development and may or may not become mainstream. It is intended for advanced users and testers who are comfortable with potential bugs and are willing to help us improve.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_heading_5 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h1 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Version: 4.28.3<\/h1><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_10 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_blurb_5 et_pb_blurb et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_center et_pb_blurb_position_top et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_content et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_main_blurb_image\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon et-waypoint et_pb_animation_top et_pb_animation_top_tablet et_pb_animation_top_phone\">p<\/span><\/span><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_container\"><h4 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Features &#038; Functions<\/h4><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_description\"><ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Estimated cut\/fill volumes in Slope-IQ designs<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Auto Nudge enabled via Settings (off by default)<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Filter for temporary loss of RTK (see Dev note) (enabled when GNSS Accuracy Loss Warning is enabled)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_11 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_2_wrapper\"><a class=\"et_pb_button_2 et_pb_button et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\" href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/app_releases\/com.AutoBotz.DitchAssist.v4.28.3.apk\" data-icon=\"\ue092\">Download Current Alpha Release<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_section_2 et_pb_section et_section_regular et_flex_section\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_row_5 et_pb_row et_flex_row\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_12 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_heading_6 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h1 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Ditch Assist User Manual<\/h1><\/div><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_blurb_6 et_pb_blurb et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_blurb_position_top et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_content et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_main_blurb_image\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon et-waypoint et_pb_animation_top et_pb_animation_top_tablet et_pb_animation_top_phone\">\uf5da<\/span><\/span><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_container\"><h4 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">User Manual Android App<\/h4><div class=\"et_pb_blurb_description\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Download the Ditch Assist User Manual Android App onto your Ditch Assist tablet so you&#8217;ll always have access to it in the field.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Includes the User Manual, Quick Start Guides, App Simulator Videos, and Emlid Reach RS3 Guide for Ditch Assist<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_13 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_3_wrapper\"><a class=\"et_pb_button_3 et_pb_button et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\" href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/app_releases\/DA_User_Guide_2.0.2.apk\" data-icon=\"\uf17b\">Download the User Guide Android App<\/a><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_4_wrapper\"><a class=\"et_pb_button_4 et_pb_button et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\" href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Ditch_Assist_User_Manual_Aug_2024.pdf\" data-icon=\"\uf1c1\">Download the User Guide PDF File<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_section_3 et_pb_section et_section_regular et_flex_section\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_row_6 et_pb_row et_flex_row\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_14 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_heading_7 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h1 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">What&#8217;s New in the latest Beta and Alpha Versions?<\/h1><\/div><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_blog_0 et_pb_blog et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_posts et_pb_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_ajax_pagination_container\"><div class=\"et_pb_posts et_grid_module\"><article class=\"et_pb_post et_pb_post_id_213708 clearfix et_pb_no_thumb et_pb_blog_item_0_0 post-213708 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-dev-updates\"><h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/alpha-release-4-28-3-updates\/\">Alpha Release 4.28.3 Updates<\/a><\/h2><p class=\"post-meta\">by <span class=\"author vcard\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/author\/ditchassist_d4bqov\/\" title=\"Posts by Ditch Assist\" rel=\"author\">Ditch Assist<\/a><\/span> | <span class=\"published\">May 7, 2025<\/span> | <span class=\"entry-categories\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/category\/dev-updates\/\" rel=\"tag\">Dev Updates<\/a><\/span><\/p><div class=\"post-content\"><div class=\"post-content-inner\"><p>The 4.28.3 alpha release has implemented a few new updates and features for testing before we roll these to the long term release: Auto Nudge is currently DISABLED by default Due to some user confusion and while we work on a few additional updates to Auto Nudge, it is&#8230;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/article><article class=\"et_pb_post et_pb_post_id_212349 clearfix et_pb_no_thumb et_pb_blog_item_0_1 post-212349 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-dev-updates\"><h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/2025-new-year-dev-update-estimated-volume-in-slope-iq\/\">2025 New Year Dev Update: Estimated Volume in Slope-IQ<\/a><\/h2><p class=\"post-meta\">by <span class=\"author vcard\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/author\/ditchassist_d4bqov\/\" title=\"Posts by Ditch Assist\" rel=\"author\">Ditch Assist<\/a><\/span> | <span class=\"published\">Jan 9, 2025<\/span> | <span class=\"entry-categories\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/category\/dev-updates\/\" rel=\"tag\">Dev Updates<\/a><\/span><\/p><div class=\"post-content\"><div class=\"post-content-inner\"><p>Beginning in Alpha Release version 4.28.0 we are testing a new function within Slope-IQ that displays the estimated volume of earth to be moved for a ditch design. You&#8217;ll see an estimated value in either cubic feet or cubic meters depending on which measurement system&#8230;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/article><article class=\"et_pb_post et_pb_post_id_212353 clearfix et_pb_no_thumb et_pb_blog_item_0_2 post-212353 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-dev-updates\"><h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/2025-new-year-dev-update-implement-width-setting\/\">2025 New Year Dev Update: Implement Width Setting<\/a><\/h2><p class=\"post-meta\">by <span class=\"author vcard\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/author\/ditchassist_d4bqov\/\" title=\"Posts by Ditch Assist\" rel=\"author\">Ditch Assist<\/a><\/span> | <span class=\"published\">Jan 8, 2025<\/span> | <span class=\"entry-categories\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/category\/dev-updates\/\" rel=\"tag\">Dev Updates<\/a><\/span><\/p><div class=\"post-content\"><div class=\"post-content-inner\"><p>In response to user feedback, we have added a setting that allows users to enter their implement with. This is then used on the map to paint more accurate coverage; the width of the painted line on the map will be to scale. This should benefit those implementing land&#8230;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/article><article class=\"et_pb_post et_pb_post_id_212338 clearfix et_pb_no_thumb et_pb_blog_item_0_3 post-212338 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-dev-updates\"><h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/2025-new-year-dev-update-idm-auto-download-and-increased-coverage-areas\/\">2025 New Year Dev Update: IDM Auto Download and Increased Coverage Areas<\/a><\/h2><p class=\"post-meta\">by <span class=\"author vcard\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/author\/ditchassist_d4bqov\/\" title=\"Posts by Ditch Assist\" rel=\"author\">Ditch Assist<\/a><\/span> | <span class=\"published\">Jan 8, 2025<\/span> | <span class=\"entry-categories\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/category\/dev-updates\/\" rel=\"tag\">Dev Updates<\/a><\/span><\/p><div class=\"post-content\"><div class=\"post-content-inner\"><p>Over the past year, Ideal Drainage Mapping (IDM) has proven to be a game-changer for hundreds of users, helping them identify optimal drainage routes within their fields. We&#8217;ve heard from many that it&#8217;s been a transformative tool for improving water management. IDM&#8230;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/article><article class=\"et_pb_post et_pb_post_id_212332 clearfix et_pb_no_thumb et_pb_blog_item_0_4 post-212332 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-dev-updates\"><h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/2025-new-year-dev-update-1-auto-nudge\/\">2025 New Year Dev Update: Auto Nudge<\/a><\/h2><p class=\"post-meta\">by <span class=\"author vcard\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/author\/ditchassist_d4bqov\/\" title=\"Posts by Ditch Assist\" rel=\"author\">Ditch Assist<\/a><\/span> | <span class=\"published\">Jan 6, 2025<\/span> | <span class=\"entry-categories\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/category\/dev-updates\/\" rel=\"tag\">Dev Updates<\/a><\/span><\/p><div class=\"post-content\"><div class=\"post-content-inner\"><p>In fall 2024 we rolled out Auto Nudge in our beta app. While we believe it was (and is) functioning as programmed (based on extensive testing), some users experienced issues with unexpected deep cuts. Upon investigation, it seems this was partly related to solar&#8230;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/article><article class=\"et_pb_post et_pb_post_id_209634 clearfix et_pb_blog_item_0_5 post-209634 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-ditchassist\"><div class=\"et_pb_image_container\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/sarcastic-sam\/\" class=\"entry-featured-image-url\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/sam.webp\" width=\"400\" height=\"284\" alt=\"Sarcastic Sam&#8217;s Farming Advice: Tips, Support, and Insights for Every Agricultural Question\" class=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/sam.webp 479w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/sam-400x284.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width:479px) 479px, 100vw\" \/><span data-icon=\"\ue050\" class=\"et_overlay et_pb_inline_icon\"><\/span><\/a><\/div><h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/sarcastic-sam\/\">Sarcastic Sam&#8217;s Farming Advice: Tips, Support, and Insights for Every Agricultural Question<\/a><\/h2><p class=\"post-meta\">by <span class=\"author vcard\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/author\/ditchassist_d4bqov\/\" title=\"Posts by Ditch Assist\" rel=\"author\">Ditch Assist<\/a><\/span> | <span class=\"published\">Jan 28, 2024<\/span> | <span class=\"entry-categories\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/category\/ditchassist\/\" rel=\"tag\">Ditch Assist Posts<\/a><\/span><\/p><div class=\"post-content\"><div class=\"post-content-inner\"><p>&#8220;Meet Sam, the heart and soul of farming wisdom, guiding with eco-friendly tips and unwavering optimism in the face of agricultural challenges.&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/article><article class=\"et_pb_post et_pb_post_id_209605 clearfix et_pb_no_thumb et_pb_blog_item_0_6 post-209605 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ditchassist\"><h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/the-rise-of-ditch-assist-in-land-leveling-a-global-success-story\/\">The Rise of Ditch Assist in Land Leveling: A Global Success Story<\/a><\/h2><p class=\"post-meta\">by <span class=\"author vcard\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/author\/ditchassist_d4bqov\/\" title=\"Posts by Ditch Assist\" rel=\"author\">Ditch Assist<\/a><\/span> | <span class=\"published\">Dec 6, 2023<\/span> | <span class=\"entry-categories\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/category\/ditchassist\/\" rel=\"tag\">Ditch Assist Posts<\/a><\/span><\/p><div class=\"post-content\"><div class=\"post-content-inner\"><p>Introduction In the vast and varied world of agriculture, land leveling stands as a critical task for ensuring optimal crop growth and field management. As technology advances, farmers globally are turning to innovative solutions to meet their land leveling needs. One&#8230;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/article><article class=\"et_pb_post et_pb_post_id_209603 clearfix et_pb_no_thumb et_pb_blog_item_0_7 post-209603 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ditchassist\"><h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/in-depth-comparison-ditch-assist-versus-the-big-company-competitors-drainage-solutions\/\">In-Depth Comparison: Ditch Assist versus the Big Company Competitor&#8217;s Drainage Solutions<\/a><\/h2><p class=\"post-meta\">by <span class=\"author vcard\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/author\/ditchassist_d4bqov\/\" title=\"Posts by Ditch Assist\" rel=\"author\">Ditch Assist<\/a><\/span> | <span class=\"published\">Dec 6, 2023<\/span> | <span class=\"entry-categories\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/category\/ditchassist\/\" rel=\"tag\">Ditch Assist Posts<\/a><\/span><\/p><div class=\"post-content\"><div class=\"post-content-inner\"><p>Explore the advantages of Ditch Assist vs big brand competitors in modern farming, focusing on tech flexibility, cost, and user adaptability.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/article><article class=\"et_pb_post et_pb_post_id_209599 clearfix et_pb_blog_item_0_8 post-209599 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-ditchassist\"><div class=\"et_pb_image_container\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/discover-the-edge-with-ditch-assist-revolutionizing-surface-drainage-in-agriculture\/\" class=\"entry-featured-image-url\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Ditch_Assist_Post-jpg.webp\" width=\"301\" height=\"284\" alt=\"Discover the Edge with Ditch Assist: Revolutionizing Surface Drainage in Agriculture\" class=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Ditch_Assist_Post-jpg.webp 479w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Ditch_Assist_Post-301x284.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width:479px) 479px, 100vw\" \/><span data-icon=\"\ue050\" class=\"et_overlay et_pb_inline_icon\"><\/span><\/a><\/div><h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/discover-the-edge-with-ditch-assist-revolutionizing-surface-drainage-in-agriculture\/\">Discover the Edge with Ditch Assist: Revolutionizing Surface Drainage in Agriculture<\/a><\/h2><p class=\"post-meta\">by <span class=\"author vcard\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/author\/ditchassist_d4bqov\/\" title=\"Posts by Ditch Assist\" rel=\"author\">Ditch Assist<\/a><\/span> | <span class=\"published\">Dec 1, 2023<\/span> | <span class=\"entry-categories\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/category\/ditchassist\/\" rel=\"tag\">Ditch Assist Posts<\/a><\/span><\/p><div class=\"post-content\"><div class=\"post-content-inner\"><p>Discover how Ditch Assist revolutionizes farming with affordable, flexible agricultural tech for smarter, sustainable surface drainage solutions.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/article><article class=\"et_pb_post et_pb_post_id_209246 clearfix et_pb_blog_item_0_9 post-209246 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-ditchassist\"><div class=\"et_pb_image_container\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/ditch-assist-user-manual\/\" class=\"entry-featured-image-url\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Color.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"284\" alt=\"Ditch Assist User Manual\" class=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/upload