reset--module--divi-button--1bffc0fc-42a0-49d1-bd9a-ae3ade2d7206_wrapper\"><a class=\"et_pb_button_5 et_pb_button et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-button--1bffc0fc-42a0-49d1-bd9a-ae3ade2d7206\" href=\"\">If you have a previous version of the Ditch Assist App installed, please uninstall it before installing a newer version<\/a><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_icon_0 et_pb_icon et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><span class=\"et_pb_icon_wrap\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">\uf14e<\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_text_1 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Navigate to this page on your Ditch Assist tablet<\/strong>. Click on the button above to download the required app version. Once the download completes, either click <strong><em>Open<\/em> <\/strong>when prompted, or navigate to your <strong><em>Downloads<\/em> <\/strong>folder and open the apk file from there.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_icon_1 et_pb_icon et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><span class=\"et_pb_icon_wrap\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">\ue092<\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_text_2 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You may be prompted to <strong>allow installs from unknown sources<\/strong> and\/or to scan the app before installing. <strong>You must allow installs from unknown sources<\/strong>, and it&#8217;s up to you if you want Google to scan it for viruses\/malware (though this can take some time).<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_icon_2 et_pb_icon et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><span class=\"et_pb_icon_wrap\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">\uf3fa<\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_text_3 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Once the app installs, run it for the first time and <strong>allow all requests that pop-up<\/strong>. Failure to allow the required permissions and full access will result in the app not functioning correctly.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_section_5 et_pb_section et_section_regular et_flex_section\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_row_8 et_pb_row et_flex_row preset--module--divi-row--5138c454-be54-4233-bd3b-f8e6a8747976\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_16 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone preset--module--divi-column--73121f80-a3ef-4484-8763-c3f18e3c56d2\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_heading_9 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-heading--ba4a6336-701f-47b8-bf5c-09da0ce28016\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h3 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Unlock Advanced Features with Ditch Assist<\/h3><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_17 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone preset--module--divi-column--73121f80-a3ef-4484-8763-c3f18e3c56d2\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_6_wrapper preset--module--divi-button--ab15fb74-61a3-43aa-96b3-41e09aeef654_wrapper\"><a class=\"et_pb_button_6 et_pb_button et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-button--ab15fb74-61a3-43aa-96b3-41e09aeef654\" href=\"\/get-a-quote\/\">Get a No Obligation Quote Now<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-212301","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/212301","targ